iproute2        is a aollection of userspace utilities for controlling and monitoring various aspects of network


Create a dummy interface
sudo modprobe -v dummy numdummies=2
lsmod | grep dummy
ip link list | grep dummy
sudo ip link set dummy0 name eth_stream_4
sudo ip link set dummy1 name eth_stream_5
sudo ip addr add 192.168.5.120/24 dev eth_stream_4
sudo ip addr add 172.17.4.210/24 dev eth_stream_4




Reference 
iproute2 -> https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iproute2

